@DATABASE "Powerama"
@NODE "MAIN" "SPECCY POKES - P - Powerama"
@TOC "MAIN"

                   ZX SPECTRUM (SPECCY heheh) POKES - P
                   ====================================

                               Powerama
                               ========



DESCRIPTION              POKE
===========              ====

@{"Infinite Lives" RXS "ADDRESS COMMAND ZXAMPoke(33791,0)"}          33791,0
@{"Lives = x     " RXS "ADDRESS COMMAND ZXAMPoke(33734,255)"}          33734,x (x= 1-255)

                         Change x to whatever value you wish, using
                         the POKE option on the ZXAM GUI. Simply
                         click the button to get the maximum value
                         x can be (usually 255).

                         I haven't tested this one as I don't have the
                         game :(

                         Rastan
@endnode
